data.description: Don't miss this great home in North DeSoto School District! Located at the end of a dead end street, on over 2.5 acres. This home features 4 large bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and a large living area. It has a large backyard with plenty of room to spread out. Carport and shed closest to the house will remain.
